WiFi & BT Module
----------------

The default |product| without the CM4 does not include a Wi-Fi/BT module. |br|
If you include a CM4 that has the Wi-Fi/BT module, the product will have Wi-Fi/BT feature.
The enclosed (|productP|) variant of the product also includes an SMA connector for an external WiFi/BT antenna, as illustrated in the figure below.

.. figure:: /Media/Pi/A53/Others/Antenna.jpeg
   :align: center
   :figclass: align-center

   *WiFi+BT Antenna*

.. attention::

    The product does not come shipped with the Wi-Fi/BT module by default.
